\description{
Reusable Quarto reporting, APA-compatible table, scanpath plotting,
scanpath modelling, scaffolding, and validation helpers for scientific reports.
}
\details{
The package is intentionally documented through the report templates and
AI-facing method notes in \code{inst/ai}. These helpers encode house style
and reusable method blocks. The general house style works for non-foraging
reports, and the retained scanpath helpers support true foraging reports.
